        <p style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.55;margin:0 0 16px;">Joint integrity is verified non-destructively on every assembly.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0 0 16px;"><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:16px 1fr;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;padding:6px 0;"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-weight:700;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.5;">2D &amp; 3D (CT) X-ray on joints</span></li><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:16px 1fr;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;padding:6px 0;"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-weight:700;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.5;">Underfill void and fillet inspection</span></li><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:16px 1fr;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;padding:6px 0;"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-weight:700;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.5;">Per-unit traceability, default</span></li><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:16px 1fr;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;padding:6px 0;"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-weight:700;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.5;">AEC-Q &amp; IPC reliability testing</span></li></ul>
